{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4ff2c723d8","title":"配合国民党军作战争取时局好转","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"675899a909","index":0,"year":1941,"month":9,"day":9,"articleId":"4ff2c723d8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2a863a3590","type":"paragraph","text":"配合国民党军作战争取时局好转","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"4ff2c723d8"},{"id":"f70a8ff250","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年9月9日）彭、左、罗、陈、刘，陈、罗口致攻湘北，又独郑、落，国民党正集中力量抗敌，我八路新四各部应向各重要交通线予以可能的委击，配合国民党之作战。同时对国民党故后各部应停止任何攻击性行动，仅在彼方举行攻击时取防卫手段。同时并向国民党各部发出通知，要求配合对故。所有上述方针，其目的都为争取时局好转","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"4ff2c723d8"},{"id":"d3bd507329","type":"paragraph","text":"毛朱王叶","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"4ff2c723d8"},{"id":"9f31344255","type":"paragraph","text":"九月九日1]这是毛泽东和东德、中共中央军委副主席王森祥和军委参谋长叶剑给彩德怀、八路军副参谋长左权和八路军野战政治部主任罗瑞知等的电报。2]陈、刘，指新四军代军长陈毅和刘少奇。陈、罗，指陈光、罗荣","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"4ff2c723d8"}],"page":{"id":"f30ad37dc8","publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"4ff2c723d8","start":225,"end":225}}}},"__N_SSG":true}